cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the software and the associated paper."
title: "UNet-ResNet + NAFNet: deblurring-aware three-class crop/weed segmentation"
abstract: >-
  Reference implementation of a three-class semantic segmentation framework
  (background, crop/sorghum, weed) based on a UNet decoder with a ResNet encoder
  and an integrated NAFNet deblurring front-end for motion-blurred UAV imagery.
type: software
version: "1.0.0"
license: MIT
