    affiliation: "College of Plant Protection, Shandong Agricultural University"
    email: zouss@sdau.edu.cn
keywords:
  - semantic segmentation
  - plant health monitoring
  - UNet-ResNet
  - NAFNet deblurring
  - precision agriculture
